{"tid":289403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(理性討論)香港P牌制度需唔需要改制","createTime":"2017-06-19T03:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T11:50:15.000Z","uid":44777,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf9610346a676751426d037a8822bc452f737f6","tid":289403,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"講真香港P牌坐完一年牌監就可以甩P<br />\n大把人係呢段時間無渣車 缺乏道路經驗<br />\n一渣出黎就做公路炸彈 一係就慢過牛龜 <br />\n<br />\n其實係咪應該改下制<br />\n例如:改長P牌時間 同分唔同級別P牌<br />\n等班友一定要拎住P渣下車 吸收下經驗<br />\n唔同P就唔同限制 唔同速度同乘害數目"},{"pid":"f1b32aeb7300edaa3bcfd51b2cd08d41b3cfca9b","tid":289403,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aebc2bf7ff76f40108552796b32a7e6289b42e0","tid":289403,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d487c8e93d80c45bfaea87744bcb4336ea24531c","tid":289403,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53a801a407e857b72e9d8179d8e5fbb9f6836cb7","tid":289403,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年p牌原意係好，不過好多人就因為咁而去雪牌<br />\n利申：p牌第一年行左10,000 km</blockquote><br />\n一年時間真係好快就過<br />\n大把人拎完又唔敢渣<br />\n但係又夠膽甩P先渣 好多時出事就係呢班人"},{"pid":"b7275b4d1187a2d556a9183bf4fd145410b0795e","tid":289403,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"根本P牌制度應該電子化,計行車里數"},{"pid":"10ceb56c7a837bf8cb0a4335035fa878c1f96360","tid":289403,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一年p牌原意係好，不過好多人就因為咁而去雪牌<br />\n利申：p牌第一年行左10,000 km</blockquote><br />\n一年時間真係好快就過<br />\n大把人拎完又唔敢渣<br />\n但係又夠膽甩P先渣 好多時出事就係呢班人</blockquote><br />\np牌本身係叫其他人讓同避佢地,等佢地慢慢吸收經驗。<br />\n<br />\n但事實係有班人專門玩同洽p牌,重危險過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a588c2cc31c413edf358d4b67d511811866e507d","tid":289403,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本P牌制度應該電子化,計行車里數</blockquote><br />\n應該行左一定里數先可以 甩P<br />\n最少嚴格少少 分埋夜間日間"},{"pid":"676d199d17fdce00978d60429332b03bac89210c","tid":289403,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f648e50023719d17d7cac56f5c56c732bdaf33e","tid":289403,"uid":3198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年p牌原意係好，不過好多人就因為咁而去雪牌<br />\n利申：p牌第一年行左10,000 km</blockquote><br />\nP左半年，行左11,000<br />\n仲增加緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedf5d9b68a2cd3d98d51aa4d134866eceb3f62e","tid":289403,"uid":56447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"洗撚咩 定例任何人 一年撞2次車 話鳩知你咩原因 就停牌一段時間 咁大家都會小小心心渣車 特別搵食車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8848914051ef296294896e259b471be93b68edbd","tid":289403,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗撚咩 定例任何人 一年撞2次車 話鳩知你咩原因 就停牌一段時間 咁大家都會小小心心渣車 特別搵食車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會成條馬路都超慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf073a6f7f530df9909b136545ff3ae4ec47843","tid":289403,"uid":3198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一年p牌原意係好，不過好多人就因為咁而去雪牌<br />\n利申：p牌第一年行左10,000 km</blockquote><br />\n一年時間真係好快就過<br />\n大把人拎完又唔敢渣<br />\n但係又夠膽甩P先渣 好多時出事就係呢班人</blockquote><br />\n有時P牌好多人讓<br />\n周不時試過想cut線有司機幫我頂住後面d車<br />\n<br />\n不過香港地亦多痴線佬<br />\n試過有人特登玩我，強行響beep cut線<br />\n呢d情況一定一野隊埋去<br />\n最後上庭告佢老不 仲要賠一大筆比我買新車<br />\n一個唔小心話自己整親條頸 生活費都賠埋<br />\nfatfat</blockquote><br />\n手車屎既，cut線咪比個五囉<br />\n朝早返工時間去將軍澳隧道，睇下新牌停定打燈有無人讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實就係你唔食佢位，佢唔會讓你入線<br />\n佢唔推我我以經即刻比個五佢<br />\n至於推人個班，就係你打哂燈，佢唔讓，你食佢位佢又封唔住既垃圾<br />\n佢心態咪同你下面個段一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa22e80a00895b51c5a2dde5a22503dcceabb7fc","tid":289403,"uid":56447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>洗撚咩 定例任何人 一年撞2次車 話鳩知你咩原因 就停牌一段時間 咁大家都會小小心心渣車 特別搵食車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會成條馬路都超慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好過撞左車 塞死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行都行唔到 <br />\n玩開P牌班仆街 都應該會安份守己番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065d249ae64cecc055a45634a0c5ce4d053f69e6","tid":289403,"uid":114513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗撚咩 定例任何人 一年撞2次車 話鳩知你咩原因 就停牌一段時間 咁大家都會小小心心渣車 特別搵食車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會成條馬路都超慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好過撞左車 塞死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行都行唔到 <br />\n玩開P牌班仆街 都應該會安份守己番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9<br />\n咁一定一堆撞車黨搵食<br />\n因為無人敢報警個個都賠錢私了"},{"pid":"d700fff479a890238f18e9eef8edc8737c054ecb","tid":289403,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗撚咩 定例任何人 一年撞2次車 話鳩知你咩原因 就停牌一段時間 咁大家都會小小心心渣車 特別搵食車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會成條馬路都超慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好過撞左車 塞死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行都行唔到 <br />\n玩開P牌班仆街 都應該會安份守己番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9<br />\n咁一定一堆撞車黨搵食<br />\n因為無人敢報警個個都賠錢私了</blockquote><br />\n照佢個意思<br />\n應該係兩邊撞都係一年得兩次機會<br />\n咁撞車黨最多咪食得兩次"},{"pid":"49779d6ffc25a55354d561bf9ecd5d7fac089acc","tid":289403,"uid":62587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"P牌限速70根本on9"},{"pid":"eaa3a7ef5861c3936ff90703e0fbb8c816ebcf37","tid":289403,"uid":16812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本P牌制度應該電子化,計行車里數</blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多"},{"pid":"adac86f8f335e92935c8e28b48801c98b15e8d2c","tid":289403,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>P牌限速70根本on9</blockquote><br />\n限渣夠一定里數先甩P好過"},{"pid":"69c4fc9c35265900ec4e664af914e6c8ddd78a2e","tid":289403,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根本P牌制度應該電子化,計行車里數</blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳"},{"pid":"5bca28a0df847e3e61502e03c49c2c9c0fea528a","tid":289403,"uid":61115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:36:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本P牌制度應該電子化,計行車里數</blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ceba3324e1483aaa8893e2f6588c7ca05710bf83","tid":289403,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>P牌限速70根本on9</blockquote><br />\n限渣夠一定里數先甩P好過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用里數限P好過用一年好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申雪P, 第時揸就算唔係強制我都會掛P"},{"pid":"5bb5f854c4f1a39bcb9a90d1db1fa664746b2ddc","tid":289403,"uid":16812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本P牌制度應該電子化,計行車里數</blockquote><br />\n不能同意更多</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n佢p牌其實都係想你有足夠既路面經驗啫，咁計行車里數咪仲實際，啲人又唔可以雪牌"}]}